---
import MainLayout from "../layouts/MainLayout.astro";
import { siteConfig } from "../config/site";
---

<MainLayout
  title="Privacy Policy | Logo Brief Guide"
  description="Read the Logo Brief Guide privacy policy."
  pathname="/privacy-policy/"
>
  <section class="prose">
    <p class="eyebrow">Privacy</p>
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>

    <p>
      This Privacy Policy explains, in general terms, how Logo Brief Guide may
      collect, use, and protect information when you use this site.
    </p>

    <h2>Information we may collect</h2>
    <p>
      This site may collect limited information such as standard website usage
      data, device/browser information, referral information, and page activity
      through analytics or similar tools.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you contact the site directly by email, any information you choose to
      include in that email may also be received.
    </p>

    <h2>How information may be used</h2>
    <p>
      Information may be used to operate the site, improve content, understand
      site usage, respond to messages, monitor traffic patterns, and evaluate
      what content is useful to visitors.
    </p>

    <h2>Cookies and analytics</h2>
    <p>
      This site may use cookies, analytics tools, or similar technologies to
      understand traffic and usage behavior. These tools may collect information
      such as pages viewed, approximate location, device type, referral source,
      and session activity.
    </p>

    <h2>Third-party services</h2>
    <p>
      This site may link to third-party websites, tools, or services. Those
      third parties may have their own privacy practices, terms, and policies.
      Once you leave this site, their rules apply.
    </p>

    <h2>Email contact</h2>
    <p>
      If you email the site, your message and contact information may be kept as
      needed to respond to you or maintain normal records related to the site.
    </p>

    <h2>Data sharing</h2>
    <p>
      This site does not sell your personal information in the ordinary sense of
      running a data-broker business. However, third-party tools used by the
      site may process certain data as part of analytics, hosting, email, or
      other normal web operations.
    </p>

    <h2>Data security</h2>
    <p>
      Reasonable efforts may be used to protect site-related information, but no
      method of transmission or storage is guaranteed to be completely secure.
    </p>

    <h2>Children’s privacy</h2>
    <p>
      This site is not intended for children under 13, and it is not knowingly
      directed at them.
    </p>

    <h2>Changes to this policy</h2>
    <p>
      This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time. Continued use of the
      site after changes are posted means you accept the updated policy.
    </p>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy-related questions, contact:
      <a href={`mailto:${siteConfig.supportEmail}`}>{siteConfig.supportEmail}</a>
    </p>
  </section>
</MainLayout>